items.title: "We have respect for Senegal, they are a big footballing country in Africa, they are the former champions, but we are ready. My players will need to prove to me, and to all Sudanese people here and back home, that they deserve to do better than where we are. I think Senegal are the favourites, but I am sure we will give them a very good game,"
“E’ fra le peggiori tragedie che il nostro Paese abbia mai conosciuto”
